The paper analyzes the capacity of M-ary PSK transmission over both AWGN and fading channels, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT), communication systems (cs.COMM), signal processing (cs.SI), networked systems (cs.NI), and physical layer communication (cs.PHY). The focus on low-SNR capacity and practical design guidelines also suggests a strong emphasis on the physical layer, making cs.PHY a likely category.
